- `export const revalidate = 3600` — Next.js static route caching (1 hour)
- `GITHUB_TOKEN` is optional (rate limit 60/hr without, 5000/hr with) — never exposed to client
- Each repo is fetched individually (no batch API) and filtered for nulls (graceful handling of missing repos)
